ke":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T14:21:06.000Z","msg":"武大郎根本係仆街嚟，唔係洗橫手會娶到潘金蓮？！正常靚女點會屈就嫁啲咁嘅垃圾做丈夫？！所以潘金蓮係無錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"我睇電視劇個版本，潘金蓮係大戶人家做侍女，因為貌美同老爺&amp;公子有染，比夫人報復，故意將潘金蓮嫁比窮柒廢既武大郎。"},{"pid":"44755742967ae7d0d241ceab75cf107a6bcaa426","tid":2232514,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61d79ed142bf85e87d2ecc10b6e31874c589777","tid":2232514,"uid":62060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"武大嘅啟示就係窮人生仔正仆街，矮撚應該去絕育"},{"pid":"deec328731341eec9ebe10b3037e26fc6acb9854","tid":2232514,"uid":178682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:45:49.000Z","msg":"調轉角度你係個靚女會有咩感受"},{"pid":"21ee47d94baaead4ebd5bc96c135f29a2f541417","tid":2232514,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"陳同佳與潘曉穎"},{"pid":"c4cf880e55b1d536f42241b5e305004221c91606","tid":2232514,"uid":71446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"現實係你努力揾錢都唔會娶到潘金蓮，照計潘金蓮咁正一早俾個主人食左做妾仕啦"}]}